column2: In general, how much of a problem do you think you have with:  …getting into trouble?
In general, how much of a problem do you think you have with:  …getting along with your mother/mother figure.
In general, how much of a problem do you think you have with:  …getting along with your father/father figure.
In general, how much of a problem do you think you have with:  …feeling unhappy or sad?
How much of a problem would you say you have:  …with your behavior at school?  (or at your job)
How much of a problem would you say you have:  …with having fun?
How much of a problem would you say you have:  …getting along with adults other than (your mother and/or your father)?
How much of a problem do you have:  …with feeling nervous or afraid?
How much of a problem do you have:  …getting along with your sister(s) and/or brother(s)?
How much of a problem do you have:  …getting along with other kids your age?
How much of a problem would you say you have:  …getting involved in activities like sports or hobbies?
How much of a problem would you say you have:  …with your school work (doing your job)?
How much of a problem would you say you have:  …with your behavior at home?
